OL,3,CFootball club pay tribute to youth
OL,4,Cteam manager who died at presentation
OL,5,Cevening
OL,7,FA youth team manager at a North
OL,8,FLincolnshire football club has died
OL,9,Fafter a medical emergency at the
OL,10,Fteam's presentation day for junior
OL,11,Fplayers.
OL,13,FAndrew Casey was under 14s manager at
OL,14,FBrigg Town FC, who today announced his
OL,15,Fdeath in a tribute to him on social
OL,16,Fmedia.
OL,18,FThe club wrote: "Despite the immediate
OL,19,Fassistance given at the scene and the
OL,20,Fbest efforts of the emergency
OL,21,Fservices, Andrew sadly passed away.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
