FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1779041472
OL,3,CFootball club pay tribute to youth
OL,4,Cteam manager who died at presentation
OL,5,Cevening
OL,7,F"Andrew was more than just a coach to
OL,8,Four club. He was a dedicated manager,
OL,9,Fa friendly face to everyone he met,
OL,10,Fand someone who gave so much of his
OL,11,Ftime and energy to his players and the
OL,12,Fwider club community."
OL,14,FThe club say his commitment and
OL,15,Fkindness have made a lasting impact on
OL,16,Fcountless young people and families.
OL,18,FThey continued: "He will be deeply
OL,19,Fmissed by all who had the privilege of
OL,20,Fknowing him.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
