FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1779041472
OL,3,CFootball club pay tribute to youth
OL,4,Cteam manager who died at presentation
OL,5,Cevening
OL,7,F"Our thoughts, prayers, and heartfelt
OL,8,Fcondolences are with Andrew's family,
OL,9,Ffriends, players, and everyone
OL,10,Faffected by this heartbreaking loss."
OL,12,FOther teams in the local area passed
OL,13,Fon their condolences to the club.
OL,14,FParks AFC, based in Hull wrote: "We
OL,15,Fsend our love to everyone involved
OL,16,Fwith your club but also his friends
OL,17,Fand family."
OL,19,FWhile Lowlands Juniors FC wrote: "Our
OL,20,Fthoughts are with your whole club and
OL,21,Fcondolences to Andrew and his family."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
